{
  "stem": "1033.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I didn't see any experiments, but they were there, they were children, even younger than I was, and I was 14 at the time.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I was even 14 when I was liberated.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "I wasn't 15 yet.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Within three weeks I became 15.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I'm jumping the gun.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "At the very end of the camp was-- on one side, closer to the [GERMAN] camp, was a disinfectant unit.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It was a kind of place where if you had a sore or a cut or anything, they could give you some sort of attention-- medical attention.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And it is of this unit that my uncle was head of.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we had food once a day, and that was done by-- they handed a square-shaped, almost like a brick-shaped, bread-- very heavy-- to five of us.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was handed out, and it maybe had some margarine or some honey or something with it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "We each got one.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And we very carefully-- that was a ritual-- cut it into equal pieces.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And people took their part and they ate it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And that was it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "That was once a day.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "The soup that was served-- I could never eat.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I just couldn't eat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And apart from that, there was coffee in the morning.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was the daily routine for food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I remember as we got there, we used to get together, and for hours we used to recall how our mothers or grandmothers or aunts baked, and the smells and the whipped cream and the butter and the meat.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there we sat, salivating like crazy and remembering all the good flavors.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But after about a month, this stopped.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And people went into themselves more and more.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You seemed to somehow-- you're sucked up by your own being.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you're cognizant of people around you, and they're all shadows, dragging themselves, breathing like yourself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But there is very little interaction, what you would call, except lining up for appels, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And one thing that, of course, I cannot forget-- the first selection inside the gypsy camp came on Rosh Hashanah of 1944.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was-- I don't think it was by accident.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I was selected to-- because by then, I was very skinny.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And Mengele pointed one way, and I saw that all the skinny people went in one group and the fat ones, or the better, not as skinny, on the other.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And behind him, I scooted into the other group.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I manage to get away with it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Somebody else did it minutes after me, and he was caught and thrown back in the other group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And these people were locked up in a block for a day or two, and then that was a [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Bells ringing, and that meant nobody was allowed to come out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when it ended, that block was emptied.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Trucks came-- you could hear trucks coming-- and they were gone.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And when this same thing happened two weeks later, many of the people had a skin condition.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And somehow or other, Mengele was convinced to give them another chance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I was in that group, unfortunately.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And in that group, I got caught.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they locked us up in one of these blocks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And there was a boy with me whose brother was still on the other side.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "His name was [?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Vol ?] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And he was from [INAUDIBLE], the same village as my grandmother's family came from, my grandmother's parents.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And strangely enough, his name was also [?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "Vol, ?] but no relationship.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And I remember, suddenly the door opened, and there was a young man throwing his arms and screaming.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that was my grandmother's brother saying, George, come and run.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And I took up and I went like a shot.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And then the following morning, that whole block was emptied.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But as I was running out, I remember this boy shouting after me, 'Tell my brother to get my ration.' Because in this place, we didn't get anything.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And that felt like, you know, what a rip off, because we were singled out for-- what do you call-- unusual punishment.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But one [INAUDIBLE] I cannot understand that, or certainly find it hurts one's sense of justice or fairness.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "It's really ludicrous at this point for even-- to remember it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "But nonetheless, these feelings were very real.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "After this incident, every night we could hear the guns in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And we were hoping that the war would be over, but it wasn't.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And after this incident, the very first opportunity I managed to get, I got into a labor group.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "They were calling for people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Myself, and as I found later, three other kids got into this group.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
